
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lv">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>YourCasting</title>
<style>
/* Vispārīgs dizains */
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background-color: #f9f9f9;
  text-align: center;
}

/* Header ar logo */
header {
  background-color: #111;
  color: white;
  padding: 40px 0;
}

.logo {
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: bold;
}

/* Container */
.container {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: auto;
  padding: 20px;
}

/* Galerija ar 3 bildēm */
.gallery {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 30px;
}

.gallery img {
  width: 300px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.gallery img:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* Iepazīstināšanas teksts */
.about {
  margin-top: 40px;
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #333;
}

/* Kontakti */
.contact {
  margin-top: 50px;
  padding: 30px;
  background-color: #222;
  color: white;
}

.contact p {
  margin: 8px 0;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
  margin-top: 30px;
  padding: 15px;
  color: #777;
  font-size: 14px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo">YourCasting</div>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <h1>Laipni lūdzam!</h1>

  <div class="about">
    <p>
      YourCasting ir platforma, kas palīdz atrast talantus un jaunus projektus.
      Mēs savienojam radošus cilvēkus ar iespējām filmu, reklāmu un digitālajos projektos.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>Mūsu projekti</h2>
  <div class="gallery">
    <img src="https://picsum.photos/500/300?1" alt="Projekts 1">
    <img src="https://picsum.photos/500/300?2" alt="Projekts 2">
    <img src="https://picsum.photos/500/300?3" alt="Projekts 3">
  </div>

</div>

<div class="contact">
  <h2>Kontakti</h2>
  <p>Email: info@yourcasting.com</p>
  <p>Instagram: @yourcasting</p>
  <p>Telefons: +371 00000000</p>
</div>

<footer>
  © 2026 YourCasting
</footer>

</body>
</html>
